data.title: 2006) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: CECIL EARL TURNER, 67, of Edmond, Oklahoma, passed away Monday, November 6, 2006, in Oklahoma City.  Services will be held at 2:00 p.m., Wednesday, November 8, 2006, at the First Baptist Church, Marlow, with Brother John Aldridge officiating.
